message.content: This paper belongs to the arXiv CS sub-category "cs.CL" (Computation and Language). Other likely sub-categories include "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval), "cs.LG" (Machine Learning), "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence), and "cs.NE" (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The reasoning behind this is that the paper discusses a question answering system using a neural network, which falls under the scope of Computation and Language. Information Retrieval is also a possibility since the system is retrieving information from the DBpedia repository. Machine Learning, Artificial Intelligence, and Neural and Evolutionary Computing are also likely sub-categories given the use of a neural network in the system.
